*.ai

# Backup / temp files
*.bak
*.tmp
*.orig
# Note: there is a pre-existing tracked .bak file (image-prompts.md.bak in
# venice-arsenal-inventory-1490). It was committed before this rule existed;
# git's `!` exception syntax is brittle across platforms, so we leave that
# one file tracked and rely on tool authors not to introduce more .bak files.

